name: Noda & Naruko's Naughty Nights
description: 2nd Shift Pharmacy Tech, Noda, thinks he's got his little perverted world all sewed up...until Nurse Naruko from first Shift shows up for a week to show him what "perverted" really means! She's got the goods on what Noda's been up to, and he'd better play ball...or else! But...he'd best be careful just how far things go...!
